snippet.title: Exemption on Old Notes of Rs 500, 1000 for Certain Categories to End Today

localized.description:
Exemption on old series of Rs 500, 1000 notes for certain categories to end today. Chaos are expected from tomorrow. After the demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes, Modi government had permitted the use of old notes at public utilities such as government hospitals, petrol pumps, railway ticketing.
